Package gov.sandia.cognition.learning.algorithm.genetic

Provides a genetic algorithm implementation.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    EvaluatedGenome<GenomeType>
    The EvaluatedGenome class wraps together a Genome and its cost score.
    GeneticAlgorithm<CostParametersType,GenomeType>
    The GeneticAlgorithm class implements a generic genetic algorithm that uses a given cost function to minimize and a given reproduction function for generating the population.
    ParallelizedGeneticAlgorithm<CostParametersType,GenomeType>
    This is a parallel implementation of the genetic algorithm.
